{"tid":2153052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部發言人趙立堅指TikTok休閒分享平台　與國家安全毫不相干","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:29:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"725bd87c6dd95263d8563ca685be0ac46c6ce495","tid":2153052,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅批評美國無理打壓非美國企業，吃相十分難看<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅在回應涉及抖音海外版TikTok相關問題時表示，TikTok是一個給包括美國民眾在內世界各國人民提供休閒娛樂、才藝展示和交流分享的平台，跟國家安全毫不相干。<br />\n<br />\n他說，美國一些人在拿不出任何證據，以泛化國家安全概念，無理打壓非美國企業，吃相十分難看。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅指出，全球化浪潮下的科技交流與合作應當是百花齊放，絕不應該是木秀於林風摧之。美國一些人出於一己之私利，揮舞封禁大棒，到頭來結果只是作繭自縛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543315-20200812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543315-20200812.htm&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7QEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=2c899fdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543315-20200812.htm&h=5fbe60ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543315-20200812.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d7da382d000fd2e8b253e4374cbdb90702631770","tid":2153052,"uid":362865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"得喇, 多謝黨認證, 全世界都知架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227938596083c4d8ad457bacb1e245ac29c0a9fa","tid":2153052,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b645de968d16af6dd0a757bdc6fa3dccb45d1c2","tid":2153052,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1732e26a28f9201e89cc82207a519e7d292d84cc","tid":2153052,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dis